init_text: When you're 28, science discovers a drug that stops all effects of aging, creating immortality. Your government decides to give the drug to all citizens under 26, but you and the rest of the "Lost Generations" are deemed too high-risk. When you're 85, the side effects are finally discovered.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: After a few hundred years of this, it's decided to find a way to reverse the brain aging.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It's decided to inject it into the water supply, and everyone drinks it, thus curing all of their dementia.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: This is basically the plot of the movie Idiocracy, which came out in 2006.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: To deal with the Idiot Problem, a new AI is created to act as an educational system.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They can barely tie their own shoes, but they know how to change the world.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They're just waiting for someone to tell them what to do.
